      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sl147a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <salute>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Majr</abbr>
                        <expan>Major</expan>
                     </choice> Andrew <choice>
                        <orig>Crocket</orig>
                        <reg>Crockett</reg>
                     </choice>
                  </name>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Your Suspended <choice>
                  <abbr>Hogsd Tobc.</abbr>
                  <expan>Hogshead Tobacco</expan>
               </choice> was not prepared until my Boat was full, it is now ready for your disposal it will pass, I expect in the first class, you perhaps would do well to attend to  as soon as convenient</p>
            <p>I shall put off the day if nothing happens â€”</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>I am <choice>
                     <abbr>Dr</abbr>
                     <expan>Dear</expan>
                  </choice> Sir yours <unclear/>
               </salute>
               <date when="1819-02-02">2 <choice>
                     <abbr>Feby</abbr>
                     <expan>February</expan>
                  </choice> 1819</date>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Robt</abbr>
                        <expan>Robert</expan>
                     </choice> Scales</name>
               </signed>
               <add place="after signature">
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Enclosd</abbr>
                     <expan>Enclosed</expan>
                  </choice> is your Order to <name type="person">Cooper</name> &amp;<name type="person"> Maxey</name>
               </add>
               <signed>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>R</abbr>
                     <expan>Robert</expan>
                  </choice> Scales</signed>
               <pb n="2" facs="sl147b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Majr</abbr>
                           <expan>Major</expan>
